{"tid":155731,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登有愛]俾我係度發洩下可以嗎","createTime":"2017-03-14T09:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T08:18:34.000Z","uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85f211f21e9a46a48cdfb9b17eefa84d0cbc2907","tid":155731,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"入左依間細security公司就五個月,職位就programmer<br />\n啱啱入黎個時除左外之外仲有兩個programmer但都先後走左<br />\n起初入黎都望懷希望覺得學到好多野<br />\n但兩個同事走左之後惡夢就黎啦<br />\n<br />\n大家都知好多老細都當it狗唔係人,我都冇例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫老細搞掂左個佢聲稱做左年幾都未搞掂既web reporting portal 之後佢就好似痴左線咁係咁俾新野我做<br />\n最過分係俾個app 我跟,而個app大至上就係combine 一個新既simple app 同另一個app<br />\n過左一個星期我未搞掂,佢就話我冇做過野,我同佢講冇咁快做到,佢就問我點解做唔到,又話依個唔得試另一個,到最後要我平行地係一個星期之內做三個apps俾佢真係痴撚線<br />\n就算你攞出去俾program公司做都要一至兩個月,仲要係成間公司做,唔係好似我咁得一條友on99咁<br />\n之後話俾錢我上堂 個堂都唔平要萬幾蚊 我起初話好 之後就仲過分 好似老馮咁一定做得到啲野俾佢 要求越黎越無理<br />\n之後真係頂唔信同佢講我唔上堂 順便辭職<br />\n而家依個月就日日chur9我 今朝仲接左個新project 又係叫我寫個app 問我兩個星期搞唔搞得掂 真係痴撚線<br />\n我同佢講話唔得 因為個app既workload都幾大同埋得我自己一條友一定做唔晒 跟住黑鳩我面<br />\n而家又數返之前app單野問點解唔得要我做返份document俾佢 講佢又唔撚明唉<br />\n<br />\n係咪個個老細都係咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：人工得11k"},{"pid":"82c5e2b9e2d49bf5a5e8c4f4ee12eba5d6f110fb","tid":155731,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"Too long"},{"pid":"5dd2a6ed9edcebbea516fb10e7a544815f5c2f4a","tid":155731,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"之後真係頂唔信同佢講我唔上堂 順便辭職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁仲乜仲要做 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeefcc4b8bad73c490fad3c79882924a608d902d","tid":155731,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"11k  programmer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbd4004111eaddc33813facdc73c774268152b1","tid":155731,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"仲有最撚過分係佢唔知係電腦裝撚左咩 係佢部機會mon撚到我做緊咩 有次就放工做晒野上youtube 佢cap我圖問我做緊咩真係痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n仲有我用自己手指過返自己做過既app, 文件<br />\n唔知點解佢會知我過左野落手指 要我攞出黎逐個file睇逐個dele 話唔可以攤公司野走 喂大佬呀明明我做架攞返黎做reference都唔得"},{"pid":"613ddb7893fa1b78062e36f438045be6b42e79e9","tid":155731,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"你都唔想其他巴打受害吧~ <br />\n<br />\n開名LA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec68deb89892c3ed13480d05768316f71a7f7a2c","tid":155731,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之後真係頂唔信同佢講我唔上堂 順便辭職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁仲乜仲要做 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家等一個月就走得 唔通返到唔做野又要俾佢閪咩"},{"pid":"90f678dd77c359eee1bc68edc9f3ad394e196fc7","tid":155731,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>11k  programmer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇好工推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d990cc5313a6f559683da0882070acccd7562ec","tid":155731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}